Author: Jeremy Garnett
Subject: Near perfect app
Body: I was very glad to find this app, especially for it's simple yet effective action.

Author: Luke Peterson
Subject: Near Perfect
Body: Need more accurate than whole number display in status bar. Going to at least a tenth would make this a 5.0 star app. &lt;-- See what I did there?

Author: Inga Aldís
Subject: Does not work the way I hoped
Body: This is just what I was looking for, tiny speedometer I can see in the status bar, but I want it to work right. I was sitting on the sofa as lazy as it gets and this speedometer said I was going 7.3km/h... not as accurate as I hoped. And one more thing, It's a bit too simple, but simple can be good. This app would be perfect if you fix just this one problem

Author: Daniel H
Subject: Great simple app
Body: This handy app let's me know how fast I am going when biking. Works great while trying to hatch eggs in PokémonGO  (even though PokémonGO is horribly broken at the moment, no tracking FTL)

Author: Job Peters
Subject: useful app
Body: but what I would like is some more options like the amount of decimals showing in the statusbar.

Author: stergios ps
Subject: Πολυ καλο
Body: Κανει αυτο ακριβως που διαφημιζει και .. δωρεαν !(πιθανη εφαρμογη σε pokemon go)

Author: Fisch1103
Body: Tut genau was es soll. Danke.

Author: Alexander Lehner
Subject: Gefällt mir
Body: Nur die Schrift ist nicht optimal zu lesen und Autostart fehlt

Author: Joe Stein
Subject: Great little App, but...
Body: This App's got exactly what I need: my current speed in the status bar. Unfortunately the font is barely readable.

Author: Иван Иванович
Body: Маленькое и очень нужное приложение для Ingress и PokemonGo. Маленькая просьба - сделайте управление шрифтами в статусбаре (цвет, тип). Лично мне нравится как на цифровых часах (а цвет - насыщенный синий). В качестве предложения - изменение цвета при превышении скорости (10 км/час для Poemon и 20 для Ingress)
